        "summary":  "AWS CISO Amy Herzog outlined AWS\u0027s approach to safely deploying Anthropic\u0027s Claude Fable 5 on Amazon Bedrock, describing the security balance between enabling defenders to leverage cyber-capable models and preventing adversarial misuse. The article details Project Glasswing, an industry collaboration to refine guardrails for advanced model classes, and a fallback mechanism that routes to Opus 4.8 when Fable 5\u0027s guardrails activate. Anthropic\u0027s published severity-level protocols for addressing reported model issues are cited as a key element of the responsible release framework.",
